    <who name="Steffen Pingel">steffen.pingel</who>
    <bug_when>2013-04-03 18:01:32 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Query jobs use the user flag of the job to control whether password prompts are shown. This allows synchronization jobs to run in the background and fail without disrupting workflows. All other jobs such as task submissions respect the user flag in the same manner.</thetext>
